Package: serial-example
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Serial port reader and writer
 A multithreaded serial port communication program that sends and receives data over a serial port.
 It supports configurable baud rates, frame synchronization, and change notifications.
